result.execSummary:
The defendant Cadias Dubage Dumellow Jackson was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Cadias Dubage Dumellow Jackson is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Cadias Dubage Dumellow Jackson was found guilty of Manufacture/Deliver THC (<=200g), a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1)(h)1.
